AI-ASSISTED THERAT DETECTION DASHBOARD
_______________________________________

PROJECT STATEMENT:
__________________
This project aims to develop an AI-powered cybersecurity monitoring and threat detection platform that assists security analysts in identifying, prioritizing, and responding to potential cyber threats through intelligent analytics and real-time security monitoring. By leveraging machine learning algorithms, threat intelligence feeds, anomaly detection techniques, and security event analytics, the platform provides actionable insights into organizational cybersecurity risks.
The system continuously analyzes security events, attack indicators, vulnerability information, and threat intelligence data to identify suspicious activities, emerging attack patterns, and high-risk security incidents. Through AI-assisted risk scoring and threat prioritization mechanisms, cybersecurity teams can focus on the most critical threats and improve incident response effectiveness.
An interactive dashboard serves as the central monitoring interface, providing visibility into threat severity levels, attack trends, security posture metrics, and operational risk.


